<p>A <code>RedOrangeYellowGreenBluePickerButton</code> is one
  option inside a
  <a href="/components/red-orange-yellow-green-blue-picker/"><code>RedOrangeYellowGreenBluePicker</code></a>.
  Each button is a <code>&lt;button role="radio"&gt;</code> with
  a <code>data-status</code> attribute of
  <code>"red" | "orange" | "yellow" | "green" | "blue"</code>
  that the example CSS uses to colour the border and the selected
  background.</p>

<p>See the <a href="/components/red-orange-yellow-green-blue-picker/">Picker
  demo</a> for composed examples.</p>
